name: CarFinance.com
tag_list: auto-loans, car-loans, car-financing, bad-credit-auto-loans, used-car-finance, auto-loan-calculator
overview:
CarFinance.com is revolutionizing the way people buy cars. No longer do car buyers need to seek financing at the dealership; instead within the comfort of their homes, they can apply online for a car loan.

With over twenty years experience in the automotive industry, our CEO Jim Landy and COO Dennis Morris have designed a company that empowers car buyers with financing and knowledge beforehand to turn their car purchasing experience into a truly satisfying event.

Headquartered in Irvine, California, CarFinance.com provided auto loans for new and used car purchases outside the walls of the dealer so you can enjoy the power of being a cash buyer when you step into the dealership. Cash buyers have the freedom to shop for the car they want at the price they want and with the dealer they want to negotiate with.

Our staff has helped thousands of customers get into a car or truck of their dreams. We specialize in financing vehicle loans for all credit types, including customers with less than perfect credit.
